data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own for less than rent! Charming 2 story with lots of original woodwork. 3 bedroom and 2 full bathrooms. Cute enclosed porch on the rear of the home. Oversized 1 car garage with a second level that could be finished or used for storage. Driveway entry from Mt Vernon Road or the alley behind the house.
